node.text: MSU is a place full of possibilities, promise and people determined to make a difference. You are part of something bigger here. And when you leave, you will be ready to change the world. Because you are a Spartan, and Spartans Will.

node.accessibility_caption: New East Lansing buildings and patio tables and chairs on the right and trees on the left with a street center

node.text: East Lansing is looking better than ever, and we can’t wait for you to be here, experience everything new and feel at home at your favorites. 💚

node.accessibility_caption: New East Lansing buildings and patio tables and chairs on the right and trees on the left with a street center
Purple and blue artwork on the right, Broad Art Museum artwork on the left and a sidewalk center
The view of Spartan Stadium, lots of treetops and campus from the rooftop of the Graduate Hotel
East Lansing buildings, patio chairs, string lights and trees downtown
Shadows and buildings downtown from a rooftop view
View of downtown buildings from the sidewalk
Photo by Michigan State University on August 13, 2021. May be an image of tree, outdoors and text.

node.text: We can’t wait to welcome you back and welcome you home, Spartans. Because home isn’t where you’re from – it’s where you belong.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Michigan State University on August 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Û STADIUM SPARTAN'.
Aerial view of campus with Beaumont Tower in view.

node.text: This campus is special, but it’s at its best when we are together. We’re ready for fall. For a new year. And for you to be on the banks of the Red Cedar and know you’re part of something bigger here. We’ve missed you, Spartans. Campus is special because of you.

node.accessibility_caption: Aerial view of campus with Beaumont Tower in view.
Aerial view of campus with Spartan Stadium in view.
Photo by Michigan State University on August 10, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, dog and outdoors.
Photo by Michigan State University on August 09, 2021. May be an image of nature.
White flowers in front a campus building

node.text: Just a little MSU campus magic. ✨

node.accessibility_caption: White flowers in front a campus building
Aerial shot of Beaumont Tower from above
Flowers surround a black bench while a fountain stream of water shoots up
The stadium Spartan helmet logo as seen from the bridge
Photo of a lantern in front of the MSU Alumni Chapel on a summer day.

node.text: Sing our love for alma mater...🎶
